How To Install GNOME On Triaxis
Make sure you are on base with no desktop environment
1 run doas pacman -S gnome gnome-extra; sudo pacman -S gdm; sudo systemctl enable gdm; sudo systemctl start gdm
2 Login To GNOME
3 Run doas pacman -S gnome-console
4 Run doas pacman -S gnome-software gnome-shell-extensions gnome-tweaks gnome-backgrounds
5 Install GNOME Apps
doas pacman -S nautilus gedit gnome-system-monitor gnome-control-center -y
doas pacman -S gnome-tweaks gnome-control-center gnome-calculator gnome-disk-utility gnome-screenshot -y
doas pacman -S gnome-weather gnome-maps gnome-clocks gnome-contacts gnome-photos -y
doas pacman -S gnome-calendar gnome-chess gnome-sudoku gnome-tetravex gnome-mines gnome-robots gnome-nibbles -y
